<%# Dr. Maysa — the founder. NeuSkin Clinic (standalone) design port. English / LTR. %>

<%# ---- Split hero with portrait ---- %>
<section class="split-hero" data-controller="reveal parallax">
  <div class="split-hero-media reveal" data-reveal-target="item" data-parallax data-parallax-speed="0.08">
    <%= ns_image_tag :portrait_natural, alt: "Dr. Maysa Al-Rashid", class: "kb" %>
  </div>
  <div class="split-hero-copy">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal-target="item">The Founder · Medical Director</span>
    <h1>
      <span class="em" data-reveal="mask" data-reveal-delay="120"><span>“I would rather treat one thing well than ten things to fill a calendar.”</span></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="sign reveal d2" data-reveal-target="item">— Dr. Maysa Al-Rashid</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- Credentials line ---- %>
<section class="section section--tight section--surface" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="specs-row reveal" data-reveal-target="item" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:48px;justify-content:space-between">
      <span>MBBS · Dermatology</span>
      <span>Aesthetic Medicine Fellowship</span>
      <span>Regenerative Aesthetics</span>
      <span>SFDA / MOH Licensed</span>
      <span>Member · Saudi Society of Dermatology</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- How I think about treatment ---- %>
<section class="section section--surface" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner" style="max-width:780px;margin-inline:auto">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal-target="item">How I think about treatment</span>
    <div class="body-copy reveal d1" data-reveal-target="item">
      <p>I trained in dermatology expecting to spend my life treating disease. What I found, in practice, was something quieter and more interesting — women who did not need fixing, only reading. The face in front of me was rarely the problem. The plan around it usually was.</p>
      <blockquote class="pull-quote reveal" data-reveal-target="item">“Skin is data. My job is to read it before anyone touches it.”</blockquote>
      <p>So I built NeuSkin around the assessment, not the treatment. Every patient begins by being read — skin, hair, body — as a baseline, and only then is anything proposed. The plan is written down, sequenced, and reviewed every quarter against where we began.</p>
      <p>There are things I will not do. I will not chase a trend onto a healthy face. I will not perform a procedure a patient does not understand. And I will not sell a year of sessions when three honest months would do.</p>
      <blockquote class="pull-quote reveal" data-reveal-target="item">“The best result I can give you is the one no one can name.”</blockquote>
      <p>What I insist on is measurement. We document where you begin and we compare honestly as we go, so progress is never left to memory or to flattery. That is the whole method, and it is the only promise I make.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="sign center reveal d2" data-reveal-target="item" style="text-align:center">— Maysa</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- The Maysa Method™ — three steps ---- %>
<section class="section" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sec-head center reveal" data-reveal-target="item">
      <span class="eyebrow center">The Maysa Method™</span>
      <h2>Three steps. <span class="em">One connected system.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="cols cols-3 reveal d1" data-reveal-target="item">
      <div class="col">
        <span class="num">01</span>
        <h3>Diagnostic mapping</h3>
        <p>Skin, hair and body baseline — captured with imaging and a doctor-led examination.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <span class="num">02</span>
        <h3>The 12-month plan</h3>
        <p>A written roadmap across skin, hair, body and lifestyle — yours to keep.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <span class="num">03</span>
        <h3>Quarterly review</h3>
        <p>We measure, compare and adjust as your skin responds over time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-center reveal d2" data-reveal-target="item" style="margin-top:var(--space-block)">
      <%= link_to "Request the Maysa Method™ Assessment", inquire_path(codeword: "METHOD"), class: "btn" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- In her words — three clips ---- %>
<section class="section section--surface" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal-target="item">In her words</span>
    <div class="clips reveal d1" data-reveal-target="item" style="margin-top:var(--space-block)">
      <div class="clip">
        <%= ns_image_tag :doctor_coat, alt: "What is worth your money?" %>
        <span class="play">▶</span>
        <span class="ctitle">What is worth your money?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="clip">
        <%= ns_image_tag :consult, alt: "How I say no to a patient" %>
        <span class="play">▶</span>
        <span class="ctitle">How I say no to a patient</span>
      </div>
      <div class="clip">
        <%= ns_image_tag :beauty_eyes, alt: "What I'd tell my best friend" %>
        <span class="play">▶</span>
        <span class="ctitle">What I'd tell my best friend</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- Closing CTA ---- %>
<section class="section" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="cta-center reveal" data-reveal-target="item">
      <h2>Request a private consultation with <span class="em">Dr. Maysa.</span></h2>
      <p>All initial consultations are conducted personally by Dr. Maysa.</p>
      <%= link_to "Begin a private inquiry", inquire_path, class: "btn" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
